{
  "video_id": "JWvFkgqeUlY",
  "title": "Reflections on the Life & Work of Jacque Fresco",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 1570.0,
      "end_time": 3788.0,
      "text": "For nearly all of his 86 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 4350.0,
      "end_time": 7701.0,
      "text": "Jacque Fresco has been designing cities of the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 8720.0,
      "end_time": 10763.0,
      "text": "This is what it looks like: a future where"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 10974.0,
      "end_time": 13636.0,
      "text": "technology is harnessed for all and money"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 13825.0,
      "end_time": 15141.0,
      "text": "has no relevance."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 15403.0,
      "end_time": 17367.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called The Venus Project, and he says"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 17607.0,
      "end_time": 20195.0,
      "text": "50 million people around the world are now"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 20400.0,
      "end_time": 21962.0,
      "text": "involved or aware of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 22100.0,
      "end_time": 23847.0,
      "text": "[French commentator]"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 25510.0,
      "end_time": 27221.0,
      "text": "[Russian commentator]"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 27330.0,
      "end_time": 29482.0,
      "text": "[Spanish commentator]"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 29818.0,
      "end_time": 31752.0,
      "text": "You may not have heard of Jacque Fresco,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 31920.0,
      "end_time": 33294.0,
      "text": "but he is known around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 33570.0,
      "end_time": 35265.0,
      "text": "Documentaries have been done about him."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 35621.0,
      "end_time": 38625.0,
      "text": "Magazine writers from Europe have written stories about him."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 42465.0,
      "end_time": 45470.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve now come to the other side of the world to Florida"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 45156.0,
      "end_time": 47708.0,
      "text": "to a place called The Venus Project"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 47927.0,
      "end_time": 50130.0,
      "text": "to meet a man who has a very clear vision"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 50247.0,
      "end_time": 53360.0,
      "text": "of what he thinks the future of cities should look like."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 54792.0,
      "end_time": 57483.0,
      "text": "Fresco&#39;s vision goes beyond architecture."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 59120.0,
      "end_time": 63512.0,
      "text": "He sees his cities as tools for fostering humanistic values."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 64312.0,
      "end_time": 67490.0,
      "text": "[Jacque Fresco] I feel that environment shapes our values:"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 67818.0,
      "end_time": 70967.0,
      "text": "the people we know, the people we identify with."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 71694.0,
      "end_time": 73512.0,
      "text": "What will drive people in the future?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73861.0,
      "end_time": 76356.0,
      "text": "A world without war, without hatred,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 76480.0,
      "end_time": 78676.0,
      "text": "without bigotry, without prejudice."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 79156.0,
      "end_time": 81694.0,
      "text": "The future isn&#39;t Star Wars according to Jacque."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 81905.0,
      "end_time": 83425.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a home for everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 84334.0,
      "end_time": 87803.0,
      "text": "Jacque thinks he has the answer in the city of the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 88770.0,
      "end_time": 91643.0,
      "text": "We’ll show a world in which values are different."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 91810.0,
      "end_time": 94509.0,
      "text": "The aspirations of people: they have compassion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 94780.0,
      "end_time": 97418.0,
      "text": "feeling for one another, concern over the environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 97941.0,
      "end_time": 101265.0,
      "text": "[Abby Martin] He’s a self-educated industrial designer, engineer and futurist"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 101460.0,
      "end_time": 104580.0,
      "text": "who truly believes the ills of society can be cured ONLY"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 104690.0,
      "end_time": 108580.0,
      "text": "if we throw away the rules that govern it and ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 108196.0,
      "end_time": 111610.0,
      "text": "A Resource-Based Economy states that"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 111236.0,
      "end_time": 114509.0,
      "text": "if you declare the Earth and all its resources"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 114778.0,
      "end_time": 118160.0,
      "text": "as the common heritage of all of the world&#39;s people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 118785.0,
      "end_time": 121300.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s no need for armies, navies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 121585.0,
      "end_time": 124567.0,
      "text": "police, prisons, none of that&#39;s necessary"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 124785.0,
      "end_time": 127548.0,
      "text": "if people have access to their needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 128327.0,
      "end_time": 129570.0,
      "text": "[Larry King] Now we&#39;ll start with this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 129955.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132589.0,
      "text": "and you tell me, you can point right at it."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 133250.0,
      "end_time": 135280.0,
      "text": "The center of a city, the nucleus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 135527.0,
      "end_time": 137534.0,
      "text": "will house an electronic computer."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 137810.0,
      "end_time": 140603.0,
      "text": "The computers do not control people."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 140800.0,
      "end_time": 142800.0,
      "text": "All the machines do"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 142218.0,
      "end_time": 145672.0,
      "text": "is control the physical entities that comprise the environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 146312.0,
      "end_time": 148800.0,
      "text": "You can&#39;t be human or decent"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 149100.0,
      "end_time": 151810.0,
      "text": "without the knowledge to overcome scarcity."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 152145.0,
      "end_time": 154603.0,
      "text": "[Brian Rose] He was talking about this stuff before it became trendy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 154770.0,
      "end_time": 156310.0,
      "text": "before it became popular,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 156429.0,
      "end_time": 158327.0,
      "text": "before Al Gore started talking about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 158450.0,
      "end_time": 160843.0,
      "text": "To save our land, to save our environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 161400.0,
      "end_time": 163584.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve got to reorganize our way of thinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 163738.0,
      "end_time": 166360.0,
      "text": "and reconsider our social aims"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 166320.0,
      "end_time": 168360.0,
      "text": "toward the brotherhood of man."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 168150.0,
      "end_time": 169665.0,
      "text": "If you had a free society"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 169927.0,
      "end_time": 171600.0,
      "text": "you couldn&#39;t get people to go to war."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 171883.0,
      "end_time": 175614.0,
      "text": "If you had an intelligent type of upbringing in one’s children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 176700.0,
      "end_time": 179338.0,
      "text": "they would say \"there must be many other ways of solving problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 179629.0,
      "end_time": 180900.0,
      "text": "other than killing people!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 181221.0,
      "end_time": 183447.0,
      "text": "We had him on the show, it was quite an honor."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 183570.0,
      "end_time": 186130.0,
      "text": "It was for a long time the most watched show."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 186240.0,
      "end_time": 189185.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not just an economic platform"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 189294.0,
      "end_time": 190989.0,
      "text": "or a technology platform,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 191156.0,
      "end_time": 193134.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s really a different way of looking at humanity."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 193614.0,
      "end_time": 196261.0,
      "text": "Now here they take a group of scientists and engineers"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 196472.0,
      "end_time": 198276.0,
      "text": "and they work on flying machines."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 198683.0,
      "end_time": 201257.0,
      "text": "You give them a flying machine, they use it to bomb cities!"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 201418.0,
      "end_time": 203374.0,
      "text": "So how can a person be scientific"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 203549.0,
      "end_time": 205454.0,
      "text": "if they have allegiance to their country"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 205629.0,
      "end_time": 208116.0,
      "text": "rather than to the Earth and everyone on it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 208283.0,
      "end_time": 210109.0,
      "text": "and the intelligent use of resources?"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 210349.0,
      "end_time": 211970.0,
      "text": "This would be a scientist, to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 212870.0,
      "end_time": 214268.0,
      "text": "[Natasha Tsakos] He is the founder of The Venus Project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 214523.0,
      "end_time": 217483.0,
      "text": "which integrates science and technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 217898.0,
      "end_time": 219469.0,
      "text": "for a new society"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 219680.0,
      "end_time": 223418.0,
      "text": "based on human and environmental concerns."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 224360.0,
      "end_time": 225563.0,
      "text": "The primary function"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 225745.0,
      "end_time": 228414.0,
      "text": "is to maximize the quality of life"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 229320.0,
      "end_time": 230894.0,
      "text": "rather than profits."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 231610.0,
      "end_time": 232581.0,
      "text": "Mr. Jacque Fresco."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 233505.0,
      "end_time": 236400.0,
      "text": "We have to learn how to manage REAL economics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 236523.0,
      "end_time": 239900.0,
      "text": "not for profit, [but] for human betterment."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 239420.0,
      "end_time": 241984.0,
      "text": "Then you&#39;ll see the beginning of a civilized world."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 243156.0,
      "end_time": 245912.0,
      "text": "It must be a privilege to serve members of society."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 246116.0,
      "end_time": 249992.0,
      "text": "Not that we want rewards or medals or honor for what we do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 250160.0,
      "end_time": 251990.0,
      "text": "[but] because it is just an honor to do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 252538.0,
      "end_time": 254814.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t always communicate with people."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 255127.0,
      "end_time": 258538.0,
      "text": "[Roxanne Meadows] Jacque’s work gave meaning to so many people&#39;s lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 258952.0,
      "end_time": 261825.0,
      "text": "and I feel very grateful to be one of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 262545.0,
      "end_time": 266116.0,
      "text": "There is nothing else I see that&#39;s more viable to work on"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 266458.0,
      "end_time": 270123.0,
      "text": "that would bring such positive change to the way we live."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 270778.0,
      "end_time": 272989.0,
      "text": "I welcome your participation"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 273214.0,
      "end_time": 277980.0,
      "text": "as I continue introducing this direction to others"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 277512.0,
      "end_time": 280152.0,
      "text": "while taking whatever steps possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 280465.0,
      "end_time": 281984.0,
      "text": "toward a saner world."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 282654.0,
      "end_time": 284363.0,
      "text": "And I am so grateful"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 284567.0,
      "end_time": 286836.0,
      "text": "for those who are working with me."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 287300.0,
      "end_time": 290829.0,
      "text": "♪ ♫"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 294283.0,
      "end_time": 298780.0,
      "text": "Jacque Fresco [1916 - 2017]"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 302680.0,
      "end_time": 305192.0,
      "text": "[Production credits]"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
